          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The aims of the work are to make labelled nitrate and",
                "ammonia solutions of higher 13N activity, to",
                "investigate their chemical and radiochemical purity,",
                "and to prepare carrier-free solutions suitable for use",
                "in biological systems. The main results were as",
                "follows. No unwanted isotopes were detected in 2.5-ml",
                "carrier-free labelled ammonia solutions but 1 part in",
                "1E+4 of the initial activity of the nitrate was 18F.",
                "The labelled nitrate solutions contained 13N in nitrate",
                ", nitrite and cyanide ions (85%, 3%, and 1%,",
                "respectively). Useable yields of 20 muCi of 13N ammonia",
                "and 57 muCi of 13N nitrate were obtained."
              ]
            }
          ],
